Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:36.40,Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,Dĩ nhiên rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:38.25,Default,Kuni,0,0,0,,Nhóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:39.11,Default,Naka,0,0,0,,V-Vâng?
